      "raw_text": "WASHINGTON, d. c., Nov. 90\nRepresentative Lacey of Iowa\nchairman Of the public land com\nmittee was at the White House to.\nday and said he would try to repeal\nthe timber and stone law at the\ncoming session. would not that\nhot hurt irrigation!\" Lacey was\nasked. Don't care if does, it will\nput more money IN the national\ntreasury and help wipe out the de.\nfelt\" said Lacey."
